𝐃𝐚𝐭𝐚 𝐀𝐧𝐚𝐥𝐲𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐬 & 𝐏𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐈 𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐧𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩

𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐧 𝐍𝐚𝐦𝐞: Hindu Priya Boddu
𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐧𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 𝐃𝐮𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧: 8 Weeks
𝗣𝗹𝗮𝘁𝗳𝗼𝗿𝗺: Infosys Springboard Virtual Internship 6.0
𝐃𝐨𝐦𝐚𝐢𝐧: Data Analytics & Power BI

📌 𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧

This internship program focused on developing practical skills in Data Analytics and Business Intelligence using Power BI.
The learning journey followed a structured approach starting from understanding raw datasets, performing data cleaning and 
transformation, and finally building interactive dashboards for data-driven decision-making.
Sessions were conducted Monday to Friday, where theoretical concepts and practical implementations were covered. 
Every Friday, a review session was held to present weekly learning outcomes and project progress to the mentor.

The internship emphasized real-world analytical workflows including:
Data understanding
Data preparation
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
Visualization
Dashboard development
Documentation and version control using GitHub
